These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  lawyer, manager, nurse, paramedic, pilot, security-guard
City: berlin, rome, prague, boston, hannover, hamburg
 1. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the lawyer##1
 2. the manager is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
 3. the manager is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the left of the nurse##8
 5. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5
 6. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere between the person traveling to prague and the security-guard##7
 7. the lawyer is not to the left of the person traveling to prague##8
 8. the pilot is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
 9. the security-guard is on the left or right of the pilot##3
10. the person traveling to berlin is not to the left of the paramedic##8
11. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
12. the manager is on the right of the paramedic##1
13. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to prague##5
14. the security-guard is somewhere between the person traveling to rome and the nurse##7
15. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5
16. the pilot is not the person traveling to boston##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Job           | paramedic | manager | lawyer | pilot | security-guard | nurse |
| City   | berlin | prague    | rome  | hannover  | boston            | hamburg  |

