.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-4::.
There 6 different types of food: eggplant, pineapple, pomegranate, radish, tomato, zucchini
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: june, march, october, february, november, april
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 3. the person eating zucchini is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person eating eggplant##2
 4. the person eating radish is in an even position##4
 5. the person eating zucchini is somewhere between the person eating tomato and the person who's birthday is in march##7
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the left of the person eating zucchini##8
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
10. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
11. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
12. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person eating zucchini##7
13. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8
14. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
15. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
16. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
17. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person eating zucchini##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |      6      |
| Food    | eggplant | zucchini    | tomato     | radish  | pineapple    | pomegranate |
| Birthday   | march  | november | june | april | october | february     |

