 5. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person driving the helicopter is the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 8. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
 9. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4
10. the person playing chess is on the right of the person driving the train##1
11. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
12. the person playing snooker is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |   3    |    4     |     5      |     6     |
