 6. the polish is between the argentine and the dutch##2
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the right of the dutch##8
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##8
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the argentine##3
10. the person who's hobby is writing is not the american##6
11. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the american##5
12. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the polish##3
13. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |     4      |     5     |    6     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | italian | dutch  | polish     | argentine | american |
| Hobby           | traveling        | photography    | puzzles | cooking | writing     | collecting  |

